     London, 1868. In the heart of the Industrial Revolution,  lead your
     underworld organization and grow your influence to fight  those who
     exploit the less privileged in the name of progress. As Jacob Frye,
     a  young  and reckless  Assassin, use  your skills  to  help  those
     trampled by the march of progress. From freeing  exploited children
     used as slave labour in factories, to stealing precious assets from
     enemy boats, you will stop  at nothing  to bring  justice  back  to
     Londons streets.
